=head1 NAME

Image::Filter::Channel - Extract RGB Channels from an image.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    use Image::Filter;
    my $channel = 1; #1 for red, 2 for green, 3 for blue
    $image = Image::Filter::newFromJpeg("munich.jpg");
